Every Republican member of the Natural Resources Committee joined me today in asking @RepRaulGrijalva to stop holding one-sided "roundtables" disguised as official committee business.

Not only do they violate the majority’s own committee rules, but they're also misleading. https://t.co/zHbyBkf6s4

full_text: These virtual ‘forums’ are extremely misleading to the American people. They are Democrat-only meetings being conducted under the veil of official, bipartisan committee work. This is unhelpful to finding real solutions & provides fuel for further division in our country. https://t.co/JclphlrjVq

- Economy added 224,000 jobs
- Nominal average hourly earnings have rose by 3.1% in 12 months
- 11th straight month that year-over-year wage gains of at least 3%
- 16th straight month with the unemployment rate  at or below 4%
